---
layout: base
title: Events
description: Upcoming Job Club workshops, meetups, and events for NJIT students.
permalink: /events/
---

<section class="events-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>Upcoming Events</h1>
      <p>Join our workshops, office hours, and networking events to level up your AI career.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="events-grid">
      {% for event in events %}
        {% include "components/event-card.njk" %}
      {% else %}
        <p class="no-events">No upcoming events at the moment. Check back soon!</p>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    <div class="events-cta">
      <h2>Want to host an event?</h2>
      <p>Have an idea for a workshop or want to share your expertise? Reach out on Discord!</p>
      <a href="{{ site.discord }}" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join Discord</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>